# Figma Make Private NPM Registry
#
# To configure this for your Figma organization:
# 1. Open a Figma Make file
# 2. Click ⚙️ Make settings → Figma npm registry → Get started
# 3. Enter your org scope (e.g. @anthropic)
# 4. Click "Generate key" (requires Figma org admin)
# 5. Paste the generated snippet below, replacing the placeholder lines
#
# Example (replace with your actual values from Figma):
# @anthropic:registry=https://npm.figma.com/
# //npm.figma.com/:_authToken=${FIGMA_NPM_TOKEN}
